  m_Name: WodeWoRemains
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: KyndeBlade::KyndeBlade.StoryBeat
  BeatId: WodeWoRemains
  Text: "A soft summer morning on the Malvern Hills. Wille rests beneath the Worcestershire
    Beacon. In the shade of the ancient oak, Wode-Wo's scattered remains lie where
    the fae left them. The seedling thou once raised\u2014root and branch and breath\u2014never
    to rise again. The forest mourns. The dream begins."
  SpeakerName: Narrator
